          "next": "N_HUB",
          "speakerId": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "Staging stations sit in their marked zones: reader loop, dummy mass fixture, test load panel, and the clipboard station. Everything looks designed to be photographed mid-compliance.",
          "type": "npc_line"
