            },
            {
              "conditions": [
                {
                  "key": "act2.staging.testLoadSet",
                  "op": "==",
                  "value": true
                }
              ],
              "id": "C_USE_LOAD_ALREADY",
              "next": "N_LOAD_ALREADY",
              "text": "use: Re-check the toggle positions."
            },
            {
              "id": "C_ASK_LOAD_PROFILE",
              "next": "N_LOAD_PROFILE",
              "text": "ask: What\u2019s the staging profile here?"
            },
            {
              "id": "C_ASK_LOAD_HEROIC",
              "next": "N_LOAD_HEROIC",
              "text": "ask: Who wrote \u201cheroic\u201d?"
            },
            {
              "id": "C_LEAVE_LOAD_BACK",
              "next": "N_REDIRECT_HUB",
              "text": "leave: Back to staging."
            }
          ],
          "id": "N_LOAD_MENU",
          "speakerId": "PLAYER",
          "type": "player_choice"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_LOAD_SET",
          "next": "N_LOAD_SET_SUP",
          "speakerId": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "You set the toggles to the posted profile.\nThe panel vibrates faintly, like it\u2019s clearing its throat.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_LOAD_SET_SUP",
          "next": "N_LOAD_BACK_MENU",
          "speakerId": "BAY_SUPERVISOR",
          "text": "Load engaged. (pause)\nFile reads \"controlled demand\" in correction. (pause)\nControlled: written down before you flipped anything. (pause)\nThat\u2019s what holds up.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_OOS_LOAD",
          "next": "N_LOAD_BACK_MENU",
          "speakerId": "BAY_SUPERVISOR",
          "text": "Not yet.(pause) Mass first.(pause) Without the mass,(pause) that load profile looks intentional.(pause) Like a stress test.(pause) I\u2019m not putting my name near that.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_LOAD_ALREADY",
          "next": "N_LOAD_BACK_MENU",
          "speakerId": "BAY_SUPERVISOR",
          "text": "It\u2019s set. (pause) Don\u2019t start tuning it. (pause) Or discoveries go in the log.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_LOAD_PROFILE",
          "next": "N_LOAD_BACK_MENU",
          "speakerId": "BAY_SUPERVISOR",
          "text": "Enough load to keep the loop honest. (pause) Nothing that makes it show off. (pause)\nWe want readings that look like maintenance. (pause)\nOnce it reads like discovery, (pause) you get a liaison (pause) and a whole new vocabulary.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_LOAD_HEROIC",
          "next": "N_LOAD_BACK_MENU",
          "speakerId": "BAY_SUPERVISOR",
          "text": "Somebody got ambitious without authorization. (pause)\nSmart. Fast. (pause)\nNow they're a footnote, with a confidentiality clause. (pause)\nDon't do \"heroic\" in here.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_LOAD_BACK_MENU",
          "target": "N_LOAD_MENU",
          "type": "redirect"
        },
        {
          "choices": [
            {
              "conditions": [
