            },
            {
              "id": "C_ASK_CLIP_SIGN",
              "next": "N_CLIP_SIGN",
              "text": "ask: You going to sign too?"
            },
            {
              "id": "C_ASK_CLIP_PROCEED",
              "next": "N_CLIP_PROCEED",
              "text": "ask: This is just to proceed to the aperture bay, right?"
            },
            {
              "id": "C_LEAVE_CLIP_BACK",
              "next": "N_REDIRECT_HUB",
              "text": "leave: Back to staging."
            }
          ],
          "id": "N_CLIP_MENU",
          "speakerId": "PLAYER",
          "type": "player_choice"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_CLIP_INIT",
          "next": "N_CLIP_INIT_SUP",
          "speakerId": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "You initial in the box labeled TECH PRESENT.\nThe paper absorbs it greedily, like it\u2019s been hungry.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_CLIP_INIT_SUP",
          "next": "N_CLIP_BACK_MENU",
          "speakerId": "BAY_SUPERVISOR",
          "text": "Good. (pause) Now I've got a clean line: (pause) You did it when you did it (pause) with valid authorizations in hand. (pause) That's staging. (pause) Keep it that small\u2014 (pause) anyone making it bigger is shopping (pause) for trouble.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_OOS_CLIP",
          "next": "N_CLIP_BACK_MENU",
          "speakerId": "BAY_SUPERVISOR",
          "text": "No. (pause) Put initials after the load is on record. (pause) Otherwise it reads like you signed the outcome.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_CLIP_ALREADY",
          "next": "N_CLIP_BACK_MENU",
          "speakerId": "BAY_SUPERVISOR",
          "text": "You already initialed. (pause) Don\u2019t mark it twice. (pause) Then I\u2019ve got two timelines (pause) to reconcile.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_CLIP_SIGN",
          "next": "N_CLIP_BACK_MENU",
          "speakerId": "BAY_SUPERVISOR",
          "text": "I\u2019ll sign as observer. (pause)\nI saw the procedure, that\u2019s it. (pause)\nOutcomes stay off my paper unless Legal asks.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_CLIP_PROCEED",
          "next": "N_CLIP_BACK_MENU",
          "speakerId": "BAY_SUPERVISOR",
          "text": "It gets us into the next controlled area. (pause) Don\u2019t say \u201cjust.\u201d (pause) Aperture bay\u2019s an energized work zone. (pause) We\u2019re staying on task\u2014just farther in.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_CLIP_BACK_MENU",
          "target": "N_CLIP_MENU",
          "type": "redirect"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_FINAL_CLEAR",
          "next": "N_FINAL_SUP",
          "speakerId": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "The staging indicators settle into a steady pattern that looks like calm if you don\u2019t ask what it cost.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_FINAL_SUP",
          "next": "N_END_STAGING_READY",
          "speakerId": "BAY_SUPERVISOR",
          "text": "Staging reads green.\n(pause)Test load is balanced.\n(pause)Proceed to the aperture bay.\n(pause)You\u2019ve initialed.\n(pause)On the way, keep the language boring.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
